Interface CloseRegistry

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DatabaseService
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultDataBaseService, JNDIDatabaseService, WrappedDatabaseService

    public interface CloseRegistry
    Registry of AutoCloseable objects. The AutoCloseable objects can add themselves to the registry (so a close can be triggered later) and should remove themselves when actually closed.
